Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.35,0:02:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她身體稍有不適
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛不大習慣人群
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您不必顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容後再聚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.81,0:03:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海黛小姐看到了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.67,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說您已有婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.02,0:04:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下… 今晚似乎無法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 海黛小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的情人你就別管了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵非常重視她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.61,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是疼愛寵物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要把伯爵和那種人混為一談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵和海黛小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是已經自立的成人間的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相重視對方…\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\N不要談別人了 你自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.59,0:04:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於歐仁妮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點你別說我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴族不是為了愛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了金錢和名譽而結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在介意那傢伙說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.47,0:05:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他說中了 雖然很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚不就是那回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不願意這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲·德·埃皮奈男爵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能和您談談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不陪伴在她身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和您沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不愛她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡她 當她是一位淑女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.86,0:05:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡交給我 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她的未婚夫 就該認真愛她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種說法也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了實話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太過激了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然一直如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有像他那樣真心愛上某人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.08,0:06:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛一個人是怎麼樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.29,0:07:05.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你還說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要按計劃進行 一切都會很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.55,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先你讚美她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚美？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讚美什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.82,0:07:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服飾啊 打扮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.41,0:07:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾福首席檢察官 是瓦朗蒂娜的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很令人畏懼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果落入他的手裡 小偷都會被判死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是瓦朗蒂娜的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她們沒有血緣關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\N弟弟愛德華 和瓦朗蒂娜是同父異母的姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 很漂亮的馬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他太任性了 真是丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子說留在家裡比較合她的個性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.16,0:08:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也討厭瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事 祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.58,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝·德·莫爾塞夫子爵前來拜訪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.13,0:09:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎有話對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我要去準備祖父的午飯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛上您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.51,0:09:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 順序全亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 先讓我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.66,0:09:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到一邊待著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.62,0:09:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.71,0:09:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您受驚了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在揶揄我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然這樣 什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然 他表現得有點笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想聽這些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過弗朗茲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲對您的感覺只是父母定下的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是您也是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以只要像他對您一樣對他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.66,0:10:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有爵位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安是位出色的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個率直的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最重要的是他深愛著您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會讓您幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…大家都如此自私
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.32,0:11:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在宣佈判決
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告犯盜竊及侮辱貴族罪 予以死刑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您酌情處理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.39,0:11:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有同情的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂王國的秩序 這些垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.43,0:11:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有探訪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 還眷戀塵世嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和瓦朗蒂娜相處得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.74,0:12:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你對她很冷淡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是誰這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.86,0:12:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經很關心她了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為她是前妻的女兒 就這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 速度是不是太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…馬不聽使喚了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.98,0:13:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧您 我們才逃過一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有善於馴馬的人在場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.00,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.64,0:13:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是宇宙人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.87,0:13:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.87,0:13:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇心是聰明的標誌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒請教您的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是基督山伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外子親如家人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說您買下了過世的王子的看台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是這種事情令我引人注目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只是因為沒有其他座位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是維爾福首席檢察官的夫人埃洛伊絲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到是巴黎守護神的尊夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬的情緒還很不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我護送您回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.23,0:14:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾福夫人 不介意的話可乘我的車同行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看見那樣的她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯瓦 為客人準備茶點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不用客氣 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我埃洛伊絲 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.39,0:14:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜 有客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐心情不佳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜 跟客人打個招呼都不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.49,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她真是出奇的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 她從心底裡渴望自由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只能逃避真心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.84,0:15:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很敏感 容易受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽不到她靈魂的叫喊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.52,0:15:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說大家都如此自私
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.52,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個也是 那個也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子總是這樣讓我煩惱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.48,0:15:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像她去世的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱 又封閉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓她善於社交 我也在付出努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說過她一定會早死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:07.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華 盡說瞎話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這孩子也很不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜繼承了祖父諾瓦蒂埃卿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和娘家聖·梅朗侯爵家的遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這孩子什麼也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使沒有血緣關係 姐弟也應當同等幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙像個吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華 我要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吸血鬼 吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉青白的吸血鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒禮貌的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 很可愛的小少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.59,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了賠禮 我帶您去我的秘密花園吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微不起眼的隱秘之處
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真擔心她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在的我什麼也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到藏著一個溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.12,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能只有花草才是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Belladonna、Mandragora、Datura：均為有毒植物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顛茄 曼陀羅 洋金花
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人喜愛的花有一種迷人的共同點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.11,0:17:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在美艷的花朵之下隱藏著毒物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都沒有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於喜愛園藝 對植物學也頗有愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為女人有這種興趣真是慚愧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.71,0:18:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您對毒物也感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 那太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毒物學與藥物學如同表裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼比毒物更誘人的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬間致人死地的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸起效 完全不留痕跡的毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多少嚴重的毒殺案件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不為人知地埋沒於黑夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.31,0:18:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.94,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被毒迷住的人是美麗的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷窺可不是紳士該干的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Borgia：15世紀的博爾吉亞，堪稱最早的黑手黨家族。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:19:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是俗稱「博爾吉亞之戒」的工藝品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 按下那顆寶石
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}{\fs20}Lucrezia Borgia：博爾吉亞家族聞名遐爾的黑手黨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據聞盧克利齊婭·博爾吉亞用這個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬送了無數性命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.61,0:19:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那其中包括她的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這枚戒指是夫人您的了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.54,0:19:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一點見面禮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祖父
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.33,0:19:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想遠離這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人認識我的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貝內代托 看左邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.11,0:20:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是阿爾貝·德·莫爾塞夫子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.33,0:21:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伯爵的別墅舉行的聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身處迷宮中的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與華麗而可怕的過去擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.49,0:21:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八話\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待
